り返す再演の先に、廻る輪舞の幕が上がる。「演じたはずの舞台。なのに、わたしの知らない舞台」「それが、ロンドロンドロンド――わかります」\"","date":"2020-08-07","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/14/04/294134_H5752.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/14/04/294134_H5752.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/14/04/294134_H5752.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/14/04/294134_H5752.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/14/04/294134_H5752.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":880,"total":1685,"score":7.5,"count":{"1":5,"2":4,"3":3,"4":12,"5":38,"6":153,"7":574,"8":675,"9":135,"10":86}},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":642},{"name":"总集篇","count":437},{"name":"原创","count":365},{"name":"2020","count":342},{"name":"百合","count":325},{"name":"KINEMACITRUS","count":245},{"name":"战斗","count":186},{"name":"古川知宏","count":174},{"name":"音乐","count":163},{"name":"偶像","count":96},{"name":"少女☆歌劇レヴュースタァライ","count":92}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":1247,"collect":3400,"doing":119,"on_hold":114,"dropped":71}},{"id":317887,"type":2,"name":"恋するシロクマ 「おしえてシャチさん」篇","name_cn":"","summary":"","date":"2020-08-07","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/78/cd/317887_y32xG.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/78/cd/317887_y32xG.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/78/cd/317887_y32xG.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/78/cd/317887_y32xG.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/78/cd/317887_y32xG.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":9,"score":5.8,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":3,"6":5,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":8},{"name":"GATHERING","count":2},{"name":"剧场版","count":2},{"name":"2020","count":2},{"name":"漫画改","count":1},{"name":"泡面番","count":1},{"name":"市川量也","count":1},{"name":"2020年","count":1}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":3,"collect":16,"doing":0,"on_hold":2,"dropped":6}},{"id":328013,"type":2,"name":"Meru the Succubus","name_cn":"","summary":"the pilot episode of my first original series \"Meru the Succubus